title: GraphQL Query Execution

participant Client as C
participant API Gateway as GW
participant GraphQL Engine as GQL
participant User Service as Users
participant Posts Service as Posts
participant DataLoader as DL

C->>GW: POST /graphql { query: "{ user(id:1) { name posts { title } } }" }
GW->>GQL: Execute query
GQL->>GQL: Parse & validate query
note over GQL: Build execution plan
GQL->>Users: Resolve user(id:1)
Users-->>GQL: { id:1, name:"Alice" }
GQL->>DL: Batch resolve posts for user 1
DL->>Posts: GET /posts?userId=1
Posts-->>DL: [ {id:10, title:"Hello"}, {id:11, title:"World"} ]
DL-->>GQL: 2 posts loaded
note over GQL: Assemble response tree
GQL-->>GW: { data: { user: { name, posts } } }
GW-->>C: 200 OK { data: ... }
